## Workers

### AI Gateway Proxy (Cloudflare)

LLM proxy — routes API requests through per-user auth with KV-based credential storage.

| Service | Details |
|-|-|
| Config | <{{ai_gateway_url}}/config><br>Web UI for managing provider API keys and user credentials |
| Anthropic | <{{ai_gateway_url}}/anthropic/v1/messages> |
| OpenAI | <{{ai_gateway_url}}/openai/v1/chat/completions> |
| Admin Token | `{{ai_gateway_token}}`<br>Controls user creation, deletion, and credential access. Keep it safe. |

{{#if ai_proxy_configured}}
Provider credentials configured.
{{else}}
> Visit the Config URL above to add API keys.
{{/if}}

### Log Receiver (Cloudflare)

Accepts container logs from Vector and Cloudflare real-time logs.

| Service | Details |
|-|-|
| Vector Logs | <{{log_worker_url}}> |
{{#if logging_llmetry}}
| LLMetry | <{{log_worker_url}}/llmetry> |
{{/if}}
| Auth Token | `{{log_worker_token}}` |

{{#if egress_proxy_url}}
### Egress Proxy (VPS Container)

Accessed via Cloudflare tunnel. Used by the AI Gateway to route requests through the VPS IP, bypassing WAF blocking of Cloudflare Worker IPs.

| Service | Details |
|-|-|
| Proxy | <{{egress_proxy_url}}>?`_proxyUpstreamURL_`<br>Forwards requests to the upstream URL parameter |
| Access Token | `{{egress_proxy_token}}` |

{{/if}}


